# Risk-Based Management & Advanced Review System

This upgrade shifts the journal from a simple tracking tool to a professional risk management system, focusing on position sizing and detailed trade retrospective.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Position Sizing:** I will replace the "Leverage/Margin" fields with **"% Risk"** or **"Risk Amount ($)"**. The system will automatically calculate the **Position Volume** based on your SL distance.

> [!NOTE]
> **Calendar Navigation:** The Profit Calendar will now feature **Prev/Next** buttons to navigate through months, and clicking a day will show the trades for that specific day.

